  <h1>Ontario CRS Calculator 2026<br><span style="font-weight:400;font-size:0.82em;">Free OINP Express Entry Points Tool</span></h1>
  <p>Calculate your Ontario CRS score instantly. Check if you qualify for the <strong>Ontario Immigrant Nominee Program (OINP)</strong> Human Capital Priorities Stream — no login required.</p>
  <div class="hero-badges">
    <span class="badge">✓ Updated 2026</span>
    <span class="badge">✓ Official OINP Criteria</span>
    <span class="badge">✓ 100% Free</span>
    <span class="badge">✓ No Login</span>
    <span class="badge">✓ Instant Results</span>
  </div>
